name: Custom Ombre' Service
description: I will custom ombre effect your hair for you according to the shades you request. colors outside of browns and blond are considered our "vibrant ombre' ". Hair will be colored prior to it being shipped out to you. Once ombre' service is selected send us an email through the website with the name the order is under containing a photo of the ombré you want us to replicate.  This service will delay shipping time by 2 days so please be advised.

name: Custom Color Service
description:
Want to show your individuality through color? we are now offering allover color services. Prior to purchasing please send us a picture of the look you wish to achieve so we can be sure we can achieve it for you. Send an email following your purchase to virginhairbylabella1@yahoo.com that includes the name the order is listed under and a photo if possible of the color you wish us to replicate for you.
Basic all over colors are browns,blondes,and black and are $50.
All other colors are considered vibrant and are $65.

name: Weft Sealing
description: Want to extend the longevity of your virgin hair? Look no further! Sealing your wefts can increase the longevity of virgin hair even further. While all hair sheds sealing your wefts can cut down shedding or even eliminate it. this service will add an additional day to you order.

name: Express Shipping
description:
Need your hair in a flash?? Once processing time is complete(4 business days) orders ship and arrive next day.Anyone getting a custom ombré service and requires express shipping will have their order sent out 2-3 days after order is placed and will also receive the items 12 noon the next day after it is mailed out.
Enter code EXSHIP at checkout to remove standard shipping charge

name: 100% Virgin Brazilian Silk Base Closures
description:
100% Virgin Brazilian Silk Base Closure are composed of 100% virgin Brazilian hair that can be styled in various ways. No need to bleach knots. Not only does the silk closure give you a natural hairline, it also creates a natural scalp appearance and can be parted anywhere throughout. Our closures blend effortlessly with our hair extensions finishing off your style with a virtually undetectable weave. Our closures are attached individually to the silk base and allows for versatile parting. Like all of our virgin hair, this gorgeous authentic hair has not been mixed with synthetic hair fibers or hair from different origins. Hair is double drawn with cuticles intact to prevent tangling and shedding problems that are common in low quality virgin hair.

Country of Origin: Brazil
Hair Texture: Various
Virgin Hair: Yes
Type: Silk Base Closure
Density: Light to medium hair (natural)
Size: 4" X 4"
